com.davidbracewell

Enum Language

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Language>
      • com.davidbracewell.Language
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Language>

    public enum Language
extends Enum<Language>
    Enumeration of world languages with helpful information on whether or not the language is Whitespace delimited or if the language is read right to left.
    Author:
    David B. Bracewell
